### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
###                              COMMANDS
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Hayvan Oluştur
# Yeni bir hayvan ilanı oluşturur.
# type: 0=Büyükbaş, 1=Küçükbaş, 2=Kanatlı, 3=At, 4=Diğer
# saleType: 0=Sabit Fiyat, 1=Açık Artırma
# gender: 0=Erkek, 1=Dişi
POST {{baseUrl}}/Animals/Create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
    "name": "Holstein İnek",
    "farmId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
    "sellerId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
    "type": 0,
    "breedId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
    "price": 50000.00,
    "mediaBucketId": null,
    "coverFileId": null,
    "description": "Sağlıklı, süt verimi yüksek inek",
    "gender": 1,
    "birthDate": "2021-01-15",
    "weight": 450.5,
    "healthStatus": 0,
    "isNegotiable": true,
    "saleType": 0,
    "city": "Konya",
    "district": "Selçuklu",
    "latitude": 37.8714,
    "longitude": 32.4846,
    "auctionStartDate": null,
    "auctionEndDate": null,
    "reservePrice": null,
    "includeDelivery": false,
    "totalCount": 1,
    "femaleCount": 1,
    "maleCount": 0,
    "pregnantCount": 0
}

###

### Hayvan Güncelle
# Mevcut hayvan bilgilerini günceller.
POST {{baseUrl}}/Animals/Update
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
    "animalId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
    "name": "Holstein İnek - Güncellendi",
    "description": "Güncellenmiş açıklama",
    "type": 0,
    "breedId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
    "gender": 1,
    "birthDate": "2021-01-15",
    "weight": 460.0,
    "healthStatus": 0,
    "price": 55000.00,
    "isNegotiable": true,
    "saleType": 0,
    "status": 0,
    "latitude": 37.8714,
    "longitude": 32.4846,
    "city": "Konya",
    "district": "Selçuklu",
    "sellerId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
    "farmId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
    "auctionStartDate": null,
    "auctionEndDate": null,
    "reservePrice": null,
    "expireAt": null,
    "listingStatus": 0,
    "includeDelivery": false,
    "totalCount": 1,
    "femaleCount": 1,
    "maleCount": 0,
    "pregnantCount": 0
}

###

### Hayvan Sil
# Hayvanı soft-delete ile siler.
POST {{baseUrl}}/Animals/Delete
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
    "animalId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
    "isDeleted": true
}

###

### Hayvana Medya Ekle
# Hayvana resim/video ekler.
POST {{baseUrl}}/Animals/AttachMedia
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
    "animalId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
    "bucketId": "bucket-id-here",
    "coverFileId": "cover-file-id-here"
}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
###                              QUERIES
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Tüm Hayvanları Listele
# Filtreleme ve sayfalama ile tüm hayvanları getirir.
POST {{baseUrl}}/Animals/All
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
    "sorting": {
        "field": "createdAt",
        "order": "desc"
    },
    "filters": [],
    "pageRequest": {
        "page": 1,
        "pageSize": 20
    }
}


###

### Hayvan Detayı
# Belirli bir hayvanın detay bilgilerini getirir.
POST {{baseUrl}}/Animals/Detail
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
    "animalId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
}

###

### Hayvan Medya Detayı
# Hayvana ait medya dosyalarını getirir.
POST {{baseUrl}}/Animals/MediaDetail
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
    "animalId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
}

###

### Hayvan Seç (Pick)
# Dropdown/autocomplete için hayvan listesi.
POST {{baseUrl}}/Animals/Pick
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
    "selectedIds": [],
    "keyword": "inek",
    "limit": 10
}
